# Treelivine ERP System

A modern full-stack ERP SaaS platform built for businesses to manage operations, inventory, sales, customers, finance, analytics, and internal workflows in one centralized system.

---

## Overview

Treelivine ERP is a scalable enterprise resource planning system designed with a modern SaaS architecture and premium dashboard experience.

The platform focuses on:

* Business management
* Inventory & products
* Orders & sales
* Financial tracking
* Customer management
* Analytics & reporting
* User roles & permissions

---

## Tech Stack

### Frontend

* Next.js
* TypeScript
* Tailwind CSS
* Shadcn/ui
* Framer Motion

### Backend

* Node.js
* REST API
* Secure Authentication

### Database

* PostgreSQL
* Prisma ORM

### Deployment

* GitHub
* Vercel

---

## Features

### Authentication

* Login / Register
* Forgot Password
* Role-based access control
* Protected routes

### Dashboard

* Analytics overview
* Revenue tracking
* Activity monitoring
* Real-time insights

### ERP Modules

* Products & Inventory
* Orders & Sales
* Customers
* Suppliers
* Financial Management
* Reports & Analytics

### UI/UX

* Fully responsive
* Dark/Light mode
* Modern SaaS dashboard
* Smooth animations
* Mobile optimized

